author: Fabian Leow
text: I have seen afew mosquitos during my workout in this gym. And today I finally able to kill one at the deadlift platform. Their body weight machine has been out of service like for ages. Otherwise the gyms gets crowded in the evening when everyone come after work.

author: Keith Qian
text:
I'm a long time member of AF but encountered seriously rude and stubborn staff at AF Guillemard. I was told by the staff that I was slammimg my weights. I explained to them that the hex bar they have is the wrong size (1st pic), hence it doesn't land on the rubber mat portion (it's too narrow). I was already gently lowering the weights but it sounds loud because 1 side lands on the wood.

I explained to them that with the right size (2nd pic is AF Geylang Central), the weight lands nicely on the rubber without issue. But they just insisted I was slammimg my weights without any justification.

author: Wendy Seah
text: Bad service and crowded. Better join other branches and customer service responses are slow and non responsive at times. Dirty toilet and no papers too.

author: D tuition
text:
Overall good and spacious. Sufficient facilities.
But all the weight plates are dirty, no idea.
Perhaps the staffs can spend sometime cleaning it

author: Gwen Lee
text: Worst gym experience. There are quite a number of fees this gym charges that they don't tell you until you encounter it - such as a "freezing fee" that is charged when I tried to pause my membership for one month. I've never had this problem when I visited other gyms, so idk what's up with the staff here tryna milk out every dollar from gym members. I've since decided I'll take my money elsewhere and visit other outlets instead, even if it might be further away from me. Visit AF Guillemard at your own risk!

author: Nic Tan
text:
This place deserves more good reviews.

First of all, thank you Jai for the warm welcome and for facilitating my membership sign-up! Jai provided very clear explanations of the letter of acceptance and also showed me around the gym. I really do appreciate the clarity and also the great hospitality. Thank you Jai! üôÇ

Previously I didn‚Äôt have good experience with some other clubs but AF guillemard has definitely left a lasting good impression.

From the get go, the gym is so new and nicely  done-up. The equipments were state of the art and well-maintained. The gym also most of the equipments that you need, for a wholesome work out.

The necessities such as toilets and shower cubicle is clean and well-maintained as well.

The Staffs at AF guillemard are so friendly and I‚Äôm most certainly very happy to have signed up my membership again, at this amazing gym. And this gym is definitely going to be my favourite go-to gym!

Lastly, I foresee that AF Guillemard is going to do better and better in the coming months.

Please keep up the awesome hospitality and friendliness. It really goes a long way. üôÇüí™üèª
